assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Torex Semiconductor Ltd. researches, develops, manufactures, and sells integrated circuits (ICs) and active discrete components in Japan and internationally. The company offers DC/DC converters, voltage regulators and detectors, push button controllers, LED lighting drivers, load switches, power MOSFETs, temperature sensors, and transient voltage suppressors; charge pump, battery charge, hall, PLL clock generators, and oscillator ICs; and Shottky barrier, Zener, switching, bridge, and fast recovery diodes. Its products are used in industrial/IoT and automotive product applications. Torex Semiconductor Ltd. was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
